{"id":309741,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-著名人权捍卫者郭飞雄先生法律后援团成/","date":"2013-08-21T06:33:38Z","modified":"2013-08-21T06:33:38Z","title":"维权网 | 著名人权捍卫者郭飞雄先生法律后援团成立，第一批计41人","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div align=\"left\"><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）著名人权捍卫者郭飞雄先生遭到抓捕以后，引起国内外舆论的强烈关注，《强烈要求立即释放郭飞雄的紧急呼吁书》签名联署迅速达到</span>300</span><span>多人，包括了社会各界人士。随后，多位律师发起又成立郭飞雄先生法律后援团，截止</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点，第一批共计</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">41</span><span>人。</span></p>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>中共当局对民间人士的镇压，并没有让民间社会停止抗争，相反，这次大镇压却使得越来越多的人士开始积极而勇敢地参与到中国大陆民主维权的事业中来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span><b>郭飞雄先生法律后援团第一批名单：</b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>滕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>彪，北京，学者</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>刘志强，陕西，律师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>唐天昊，重庆，律师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">     </span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>王</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>成，浙江，律师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">   </span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>陈建刚，北京，律师</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>范标文，广东，律师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>刘卫国，山东，律师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">   </span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>李桂生，贵州，律师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>吴魁明，广东，律师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>唐荆陵，广东，律师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">   </span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>付永刚，山东，律师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 